<a-card>
    <a-form style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto;">
        <a-form-item :label-col="formStyle.labelCol" :wrapper-col="formStyle.wrapperCol"
                     label="昵称">
            <a-input placeholder="请输入"/>
        </a-form-item>
        <a-form-item :label-col="formStyle.labelCol" :wrapper-col="formStyle.wrapperCol"
                     label="出生日期">
            <a-range-picker style="width: 100%;"/>
        </a-form-item>
        <a-form-item :label-col="formStyle.labelCol" :wrapper-col="formStyle.wrapperCol"
                     label="简介">
            <a-textarea placeholder="请输入" :rows="4"/>
        </a-form-item>
        <a-form-item :label-col="formStyle.labelCol" :wrapper-col="formStyle.wrapperCol"
                     label="朋友圈可见范围">
            <a-radio-group :defaultValue="1">
                <a-radio :value="1">全部</a-radio>
                <a-radio :value="2">近半年</a-radio>
                <a-radio :value="3">近一个月</a-radio>
                <a-radio :value="4">近三天</a-radio>
            </a-radio-group>
        </a-form-item>
        <a-form-item :label-col="formTailStyle.labelCol" :wrapper-col="formTailStyle.wrapperCol">
            <a-button class="mr-2" type="primary">提交</a-button>
            <a-button class="mr-2">重置</a-button>
        </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
</a-card>
